#: plugin/framework/constants.py
msgid ""
"AI: I can edit or translate your document instantly with professional "
"formatting and color. Try me!"
msgstr ""
"AI: Mogu trenutno urediti ili prevesti vaš dokument uz profesionalno "
"oblikovanje i boje. Isprobajte me!"

#: plugin/framework/constants.py
msgid ""
"AI: I can help you with formulas, data analysis, and colorful charts. Try "
"me!"
msgstr ""
"AI: Mogu vam pomoći s formulama, analizom podataka i šarenim grafikonima. "
"Isprobajte me!"

#: plugin/framework/constants.py
msgid ""
"AI: I can help you create and edit polished, colorful shapes in Draw and "
"Impress. Try me!"
msgstr ""
"AI: Mogu vam pomoći u stvaranju i uređivanju dotjeranih, šarenih oblika u "
"Drawu i Impressu. Isprobajte me!"

#: plugin/framework/constants.py
msgid ""
"AI: I can do web research to answer any question, or summarize a web page, "
"without seeing or changing your document. Let's chat."
msgstr ""
"AI: Mogu pretraživati web kako bih odgovorio na bilo koje pitanje ili sažeo "
"web stranicu, bez gledanja ili mijenjanja vašeg dokumenta. Razgovarajmo."

#: plugin/framework/constants.py
msgid ""
"AI: Deep Research mode runs a multi-step web investigation (planning, "
"several searches, synthesis) and can insert a formatted report into your "
"document. It takes longer but produces more thorough results."
msgstr ""
"AI: Način rada Deep Research pokreće višestruko web istraživanje "
"(planiranje, nekoliko pretraživanja, sinteza) i može umetnuti oblikovano "
"izvješće u vaš dokument. Traje dulje, ali daje temeljitije rezultate."

#: plugin/framework/constants.py
msgid ""
"AI: Let's explore and design your idea together. I'll ask questions, suggest"
" approaches, and help you build an approved spec in your document when "
"you're ready."
msgstr ""
"AI: Istražimo i osmislimo vašu ideju zajedno. Postavljat ću pitanja, "
"predlagati pristupe i pomoći vam da izradite odobrenu specifikaciju u vašem "
"dokumentu kada budete spremni."

#: plugin/framework/constants.py
msgid ""
"AI: Let's draft your document section-by-section. I'll help you create a "
"writing plan outline, and then implement it incrementally with your "
"approval."
msgstr ""
"AI: Izradimo vaš dokument odjeljak po odjeljak. Pomoći ću vam stvoriti nacrt"
" plana pisanja, a zatim ga postupno provoditi uz vaše odobrenje."

#: plugin/framework/constants.py
msgid ""
"AI: PPT-Master mode — I'll run the ppt-master workflow in your configured "
"Python venv (scripts + export to Impress). Describe your topic or point me "
"at a project folder."
msgstr ""
"AI: Način PPT-Master — Pokrenut ću tijek rada ppt-master u vašem "
"konfiguriranom Python venv-u (skripte + izvoz u Impress). Opišite svoju temu"
" ili me usmjerite na mapu projekta."

