"Pause after you stop talking, then auto-stop and send (Record). 0 = wait "
"until you click Stop Rec."
msgstr ""
"Pauza nakon prestanka govora, zatim automatsko zaustavljanje i slanje "
"(Snimi). 0 = čekaj dok ne kliknete Zaustavi snimanje."

